title: Women in Tech and Innovation forum to take place on Feb. 8 and 9 - Crossroads Today
content: Women in Tech and Innovation forum to take place on Feb. 8 and 9  Crossroads Today
description: AUSTIN, Texas – Governor Greg Abbott, the Texas Film Commission and the Governor’s Commission for Women invite Texans to attend the online Women in Tech and Innovation Forum (WITI) on Feb. 8 and 9. The Texas Film Commission and the Governor’s Commission for Women will co-host the forum. AT&T will present it. The two-day conference is free and will include...
